#axiom never overwrite truth with less precise truth

if new version is shorter, vaguer, or missing detail → reject or store as state=0


⸻


#axiom separate layers or lose both

story ≠ definition  
meme ≠ system rule  
tone ≠ logic


⸻


#axiom pause before promotion

generation is free  
promotion is expensive  


⸻


#axiom unknown is safe, false certainty is dangerous

state=0 preserves optionality  
state=1 locks behavior


⸻


#axiom protect the invariants

direction.db  
gematria.db  
core definitions  

if these drift → everything drifts


